messages.content: Don't make assumptions about what values to plug into functions. Ask for clarification if a user request is ambiguous.
I don’t have access to your current location. If you can share an approximate address, nearby landmark, or your GPS coordinates (latitude and longitude), I can try to identify the city for you.
I don't have any more details.

I’m sorry, but without some location information—such as GPS coordinates, a street address, or a nearby landmark—I don’t have enough to determine what city you’re in. If you can provide any of those details, I’ll gladly help identify the city.

I understand. Unfortunately, I don’t have any way to determine your current city without at least a rough location, landmark, or set of coordinates. If you change your mind and can share even an approximate reference point, feel free to let me know and I’ll do my best to help.
